---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy & Cookie Policy | NextVision Studio"
  description="How NextVision Studio handles website enquiries, analytics, advertising measurement and cookie choices."
  canonical="https://www.nextvisionstudio.com/privacy-policy/"
>
  <main class="policy-page">
    <article>
      <header>
        <div>Privacy &amp; cookies</div>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: 20 July 2026</p>
      </header>

      <section>
        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          NextVision Studio is a Dublin-based creative and digital services
          business. For privacy questions, email
          <a href="mailto:hello@nextvisionstudio.com">hello@nextvisionstudio.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Information you choose to send</h2>
        <p>
          Our enquiry forms may collect your name, email address, business name,
          project details and answers provided through the Content Growth Check.
          We use this information to respond to your enquiry, prepare a quote and
          discuss the requested service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Form processing</h2>
        <p>
          Website form submissions are sent directly to NextVision Studio's
          private CRM and stored in our own customer database so that we can
          respond, prepare a quote and manage the resulting sales conversation.
          We also retain the page and campaign attribution connected with the
          enquiry. Do not submit confidential, financial or sensitive personal
          information through the enquiry forms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Analytics and advertising measurement</h2>
        <p>
          With your permission, Google Analytics and Google Ads measurement help
          us understand visits, page performance and which campaigns generate
          enquiries. Optional analytics and advertising storage is denied until
          you choose “Accept analytics” in the cookie notice.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>External media and services</h2>
        <p>
          Pages may contain YouTube and Instagram videos, WhatsApp links and
          other external services. External video players load only after you
          choose to play them. Opening or interacting with those services is
          subject to the provider’s own privacy terms. The website is hosted on
          Vercel.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How long information is kept</h2>
        <p>
          Enquiry information is kept only for as long as reasonably required to
          respond, provide the requested service, maintain business records and
          meet applicable legal obligations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Your choices and rights</h2>
        <p>
          You can decline optional analytics in the cookie notice. You may also
          contact us to ask about personal information connected with your enquiry
          or to request an appropriate correction or deletion.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          NextVision Studio, Dublin, Ireland<br />
          <a href="mailto:hello@nextvisionstudio.com">hello@nextvisionstudio.com</a><br />
          <a href="tel:+353894797055">+353 89 479 7055</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page { min-height: 100vh; padding: 155px 24px 110px; background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 5%, rgba(155,210,255,.1), transparent 26%), #111; color: #fff; }
  .policy-page article { width: min(100%, 820px); margin: 0 auto; }
  .policy-page header { margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .policy-page header div { color: #cfeaff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: .15em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .policy-page h1 { margin: 18px 0; font-size: clamp(54px, 8vw, 90px); line-height: .95; letter-spacing: -.06em; }
  .policy-page header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.42); }
  .policy-page section { padding: 30px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(180,220,255,.11); }
  .policy-page h2 { margin: 0 0 13px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: -.035em; }
  .policy-page section p { margin: 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,.66); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.72; }
  .policy-page a { color: #cfeaff; text-underline-offset: 4px; }
  @media (max-width: 650px) { .policy-page { padding: 125px 18px 80px; } }
</style>
